{"tid":2516884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"羅致光：自己偏左","createTime":"2021-05-05T03:07:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T03:13:13.000Z","uid":112747,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1a209f1ce4147323065cadb21e6850d24eb68591","tid":2516884,"uid":112747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:07:12.000Z","msg":"勞工及福利局局長羅致光說，仍在草擬取消強積金對沖的法例，形容自己在勞工政策屬中間偏左。羅致光在網誌撰文，回顧近四年的勞工政策，<span class=\"red\">形容自己屬於中間偏左</span>，只是左邊的認為他偏右，右邊的認為他偏左。<br />\n<br />\n提到在設立法定侍產假、法定假日與公眾假期看齊等政策，被部分勞工界批評是偏向商界，同時被部分商界批評向他們開刀。他說勞工政策向來爭議十分大，不少政策爭議持續十多廿年未有寸進，取消強積金對沖的法例草擬仍在努力，目的是在今屆政府內完成立法工作。"},{"pid":"26af576721e18c9501e1be6a22f9501dfeb0abee","tid":2516884,"uid":56321,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:09:06.000Z","msg":"從你嘅言談舉止，我覺得你係偏向仆街，無中間"},{"pid":"7a9cf4158fd9fabfce785997649ff43ad6142494","tid":2516884,"uid":389613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:09:22.000Z","msg":"民主黨快撚D解散啦，匯點入面仲有幾多呢D鬼？<br />\n遲下實參選幫中共刷民意授權 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31879b0558f902aa0aad3a599b2d5e06aed0bfa7","tid":2516884,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:09:27.000Z","msg":"中共玩緊極端民族主義，仲算唔算左呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BfcnwurmpaY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBfcnwurmpaY&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK0uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=671afbfd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BfcnwurmpaY</a>"},{"pid":"6dc1310308aa4c238a6ec9d7a5e027663ce22305","tid":2516884,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:09:49.000Z","msg":"唔敢提外傭疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ed3ae0016e42f9fa3071af3a57c7a86f91f7a42","tid":2516884,"uid":2757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"